dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Kewaunee County, WI 2017
dc_description_s: These polygon and line data layers represent hydrography for Kewaunee County, Wisconsin in 2017. They are feature classes within the geodatabase Kewaunee_Hydro_2017.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are 'KEWAUNEE_HYDRO_2017_LINE' and 'KEWAUNEE_HYDRO_2017_POLY'.
